      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TICKETS (8) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 1.75 lengths from the winner Paw Ramello in second(22.45) at this track. Expected to feature in the finish again. ASTON PLUTO (4) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (22.71) at Warrnambool. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Worth following up. PENNY'S LEGACY (1) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from 10 starts. Below best last time at Bendigo (24.82) in a Grade 5, finishing a 9 length eighth. Can feature with the right run. TRICKY DISCO (6) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
